    "long_instructions": "## Journalist - Level 3: Multi-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice multi-shot prompting through the career of a journalist by giving the AI more structure and detailed expectations to guide a stronger response.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a prompt like the one below, or write a similar one that clearly outlines what you want the AI to include in the summary.\r\n\r\n>Provide a summary of the latest news on climate change. The article should include facts about rising sea levels, the impact on wildlife, and what is being done to combat the crisis.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how adding structure and specific details improved the AI’s summary.",
